admin_org_notification_email_title: Erakunde batek DNS konfigurazioa behar du
admin_org_notification_email_body_part1:
"{{orgSlug}}" slug-arekin erakunde bat sortu da.

Mesedez, ziurtatu zure DNS erregistroa konfiguratzen duzula erakunde berriari dagokion azpidomeinua aplikazio nagusia exekutatzen ari den lekura bideratzeko. Bestela, erakundeak ez du funtzionatuko.

Hemen dituzu azpidomeinua aplikaziora bideratzeko oinarrizko aukerak, erakundearen profil orria kargatu ahal izateko.

A erregistroarekin egin dezakezu:

org_admin_no_slots|content:
Hello Organization Admins,

Please note: It has been brought to our attention that {{username}} has not had any availability when a user has visited {{username}}/{{slug}}

There’s a few reasons why this could be happening
The user does not have any calendars connected
Their schedules attached to this event are not enabled

We recommend checking their availability to resolve this.
